{"tid":1134974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【網民hot talk】銅鑼灣餐廳要男顧客坐馬桶屙尿 畫公仔畫出J","createTime":"2019-05-02T04:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T05:37:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7ddfceadc53c066c70f26a594f6ce6be03e9fc98","tid":1134974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:36:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190501/large/1556717699_6eab.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190501%2Flarge%2F1556717699_6eab.png&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=f56f8471\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190501/large/1556717699_6eab.png</a><br />\n<br />\n哥哥」張國榮在電影《胭脂扣》有一經典對白：「當年屙尿射過界，今日屙尿滴濕鞋」。老男人小便「滴滴仔」，可謂苦了一班清潔工，但餐廳要求顧客坐在馬桶小便，又是否上策？設計博客「中央聖學子」日前在facebook專頁，公開銅鑼灣某食肆男廁馬桶蓋上的圖示。該餐廳警告男顧客不可對着馬桶站立小便，而是應坐在馬桶、並把陰莖對準馬桶內壁小便。該圖示甚至直接把陰莖和陰囊畫出來，「學子」笑言該餐廳「畫公仔畫出J」。<br />\n<br />\n「學子」以〈屙錯幾十年〉為題發帖，並在hashtag嘲該餐廳「#女權主義乎 #仲要求貼實個坑 #屙得準匹夫有責 #懷疑告示成效 #我犯規 #可愛的infographic」。雖然「學子」未有主動「開名」，但有網民留言「開估」：「我見過張圖，我心諗邊條X樣畫到咁X detail，好似係時代廣場金滿庭」，「學子」遂以讚好和笑臉符號回應，更謂「勢成景點」。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n有網民批評設計圖示的人「無腦」，「身為男人，點可能將支（陰莖）潛落去馬桶，支嘢掂到個馬桶就PK（仆街）了」，「學子」質疑「會唔會係女設計師/女主管缺乏同理心（empathy）下嘅決定？」《蘋果》曾在該餐廳休市時段致電查詢，惟職員僅着記者向辦公室查詢，但未能提供有關電話。而該餐廳的網頁正在維修，未有顯示辦公室的聯絡方法。<br />\n<br />\n網民點睇<br />\n<br />\nSam Maverick Mick Sam：呢幅圖好明顯針對東方人，X細！叫樓主去平機會告X佢哋！<br />\nMick Sam Dennis Ko：畫嗰個好明顯未見過大蛇屙尿。<br />\nK.C. Alvis：次次（陰莖）都會掂到（馬桶內壁），（餐廳應該）改善嗰個細到無人有嘅馬桶先喇。<br />\nMichael Au Hi：（陰莖）拭到（馬桶內壁），浸鏹水都唔掂呀。<br />\nRicky Yuen：（屙尿）一滴滴，就要睇醫生。"},{"pid":"998bfb7e4e82a5ac0b8adbdcdbf00c4c17d7bc10","tid":1134974,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:40:09.000Z","msg":"圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707e872175718dbb2b21828cfef44497813fdb2c","tid":1134974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"998bfb7e4e82a5ac0b8adbdcdbf00c4c17d7bc10","tid":1134974,"uid":232594,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:40:09.000Z","msg":"圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:40:48.000Z","msg":"見唔見到條libk?"},{"pid":"86a468b456c41352bb97b8b871ee396565ab1533","tid":1134974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:41:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>圖呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>見唔見到條li<span style=\"color: red;\">n</span>k?</blockquote>"},{"pid":"a31a885832e4f74d30d1d9fc4dfd1ffaf5eab204","tid":1134974,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"畫公仔畫出J"},{"pid":"d83ff4e39053a9dd64f6f02c46a3f68aec887c29","tid":1134974,"uid":199162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T04:44:50.000Z","msg":"畫埋春袋咁趣致"},{"pid":"288a85ac50c35ec1857d8c4d2292d2c8432db2ab","tid":1134974,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T05:06:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190502/59552226?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190502%2F59552226%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=P2v3VPQ3iBAPr6cjv61qmUzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=a929cc51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190502%2F59552226%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=a8e2e9f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190502/59552226?